title: [1964] Stan Getz - Getz Au Go Go (320kbps)
description:
1964 live set from Stan Getz Quartet with Astrud Gilberto. Recorded at Cafe Au Go Go in Greenwich Village, New York City on August 19, 1964. Stan Getz on tenor sax, Astrud Gilberto on vocals, Gary Burton on vibes, Gene Cherico on bass, & Joe Hunt on drums. Ripped from the CD at 320kbps.
